PrecisTransfer of certain powers, duties and functions of the Minister of Finance for making a SPECIAL ADJUSTMENT PAYMENT to each province, as follows: 1. to the Minister of NATIONAL HEALTH AND WELFARE with respect to both the insured health services program and the extended health care services program, and 2. to the Minister of EMPLOYMENT AND IMMIGRATION with respect to the post-secondary education program.
